This is a data engineering portfolio project: a hospital readmission risk lakehouse on Azure.
Stack: Databricks (PySpark), dbt, Airflow (Docker), Terraform, GitHub Actions, Power BI, OpenAI API.
Architecture: medallion (bronze/silver/gold), Kimball star schema in gold.
Source data: Synthea synthetic FHIR.
Dev environment: WSL2 Ubuntu, Python 3.12, uv for packaging.
The project must be production-shaped. Treat every file as if it were going into a real codebase.
